# Testing

**No test project.** Do not search for existing tests.

## When Adding

```
backend.Tests/Features/{Entity}Feature/{Operation}HandlerTests.cs
```

xUnit + `Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.Testing`. Mirror `Features/` structure.

## Handler Tests

Arrange DbContext → Act `handler.Handle(cmd, CT)` → Assert `IsSuccess` or error string.

Must cover: success, `"not found"`, `"already exists"`, delete-with-children failure.

## Integration Tests

`WebApplicationFactory<Program>` — assert status (201/404/409/400) + `ApiResponse` shape (`success`, `data`).

Prefer Testcontainers PostgreSQL over `UseInMemoryDatabase` for relational checks.

## Priority (MVP)

Category → Product → Cart/Order → Auth

## Skip

EF scaffold mapping tests, full JSON snapshots, mocking MediatR in HTTP tests.
